elements.name: As a user, I create an valid account and buy products then add to cart and verify total prices after checkout

steps.name: I want to open the URL with browser
I click on "Sign in link"
I enter "email"
I click on "Create an account button"
I click on "Mrs"
I enter the valid datas into fields at the register form
I select "the state"
I enter "postal code"
I select "the country"
I enter "mobile phone"
I click on "the register button"
I click on "logo to go to the Homepage"

arguments.val: logo to go to the Homepage

steps.name: I move to "Product 1"
I hover on "the image of product 1"
I click on "add to cart product 1"
I wait to see "continue button"
I click on "continue shopping button"
I hover on "the image of product 2"
I click on "add to cart product 2"
I wait to see "proceed button"
I click on "Proceed to checkout button at popup"

arguments.val: Proceed to checkout button at popup

steps.name: I click on "Proceed to checkout at summary page"

arguments.val: Proceed to checkout at summary page

steps.name: I click on "Proceed to checkout at address page"

arguments.val: Proceed to checkout at address page

steps.name: I click on "Terms of service at Shipping page"

arguments.val: Terms of service at Shipping page

steps.name: I click on "Proceed to checkout at Shipping page"

arguments.val: Proceed to checkout at Shipping page

steps.name: I click on "Pay by bank wire"
I verify the total price
I click on "I confirm my order button"
